948  pObj->calcBound();
949  objList2.push_back(pObj);
950 
951  // security room wall - right wall
952  pObj = new CObj (GEO_PATCH , Vector3(supermarketPosition.x + (supermarketSize.x * supermarketScale.x) / 6, supermarketPosition.y, supermarketPosition.z + (supermarketScale.z * supermarketSize.z)/3.5 ), Vector3(0,90,0), supermarketScale * 3, Vector3(1,1,1));
953  objList2.push_back(pObj);
954 
955  //wall bounds
956  Vector3 tempWallPosition(pObj->getTranslate());
957  pObj = new CObj(GEO_SUPERMARKET_WALL , Vector3(tempWallPosition.x , tempWallPosition.y, tempWallPosition.z ) ,Vector3(0,0,0), supermarketScale , Vector3(1, supermarketSize.y , supermarketSize.z / 2));
958  pObj->calcBound();
959  objList2.push_back(pObj);
960 
961  //security room wall - left wall
962  pObj = new CObj (GEO_PATCH , Vector3(supermarketPosition.x + (supermarketSize.x * supermarketScale.x) / 6, supermarketPosition.y ,supermarketPosition.z - (supermarketScale.z * supermarketSize.z)/ 3.5 ), Vector3(0,90,0), supermarketScale * 3, Vector3(1,1,1));
963  objList2.push_back(pObj);
964 
965  // wall bound
966  tempWallPosition.Set(pObj->getTranslate().x , pObj->getTranslate().y , pObj->getTranslate().z);
967  pObj = new CObj(GEO_SUPERMARKET_WALL , Vector3(tempWallPosition.x , tempWallPosition.y, tempWallPosition.z ) ,Vector3(0,0,0), supermarketScale , Vector3(1, supermarketSize.y , supermarketSize.z / 2));
968  pObj->calcBound();
969  objList2.push_back(pObj);
970 
971  //security room wall - middle top
972  tempWallPosition.Set(supermarketPosition.x + (supermarketScale.x * supermarketSize.x)/ 6 , supermarketPosition.y + (supermarketScale.y * supermarketSize.y) / 2 - (supermarketScale.y * 4.6) , supermarketPosition.z);
973  pObj = new CObj(GEO_PATCH, tempWallPosition, Vector3 (0,-90,0), supermarketScale * 2, Vector3 ( 1, 1 ,supermarketSize.z / 2));
974  objList2.push_back(pObj);

1841 /******************************************************************************/
1848 /******************************************************************************/
1849 void SP2::updateSuperMarket(double dt)
1850 {
1851  static bool trolleyNearLift = false;
1852  static const float LIFT_SPEED = 0.1 * supermarketScale.x;
1853  //lift door interaction (needed for both floors) [ closes when selected floor to go]
1854  if(camera.position.x < supermarketLiftDoorMaxBound.x && camera.position.x > supermarketLiftDoorMinBound.x && camera.position.z < supermarketLiftDoorMaxBound.z && camera.position.z > supermarketLiftDoorMinBound.z)
1855  {
1856  if (hands[0] != NULL && hands[0]->getID() == GEO_TROLLEY)
1857  {
1858  trolleyNearLift = true;
1859  }
1860  else
1861  {
1862  trolleyNearLift = false;
1863  }
1864  if (trolleyNearLift)
1865  {
1866  disableLiftDoor = true;
1867  }
1868 
1869  if(disableLiftDoor == false && !trolleyNearLift)
1870  {
1871  if(translateLiftX < 2)
1872  {
1873  liftRightDoor->setTranslateX(liftRightDoor->getTranslate().x + LIFT_SPEED);
1874  liftRightDoor->calcBound();
1875  liftLeftDoor->setTranslateX(liftLeftDoor->getTranslate().x - LIFT_SPEED);
1876  liftLeftDoor->calcBound();
1877  translateLiftX += 0.1;
1878  }
1879  }
1880  }
1881  else
1882  {
1883  if(disableLiftDoor == false)
1884  {
1885  if(translateLiftX > 0)
1886  {
1887  liftRightDoor->setTranslateX(liftRightDoor->getTranslate().x - LIFT_SPEED);
1888  liftRightDoor->calcBound();
1889  liftLeftDoor->setTranslateX(liftLeftDoor->getTranslate().x + LIFT_SPEED);
1890  liftLeftDoor->calcBound();
1891  translateLiftX -= 0.1;
1892  }
1893  }
1894  }
1895  if(disableLiftDoor == true)
1896  {
1897  if(translateLiftX > 0)
1898  {
1899  liftRightDoor->setTranslateX(liftRightDoor->getTranslate().x - LIFT_SPEED);
1900  liftRightDoor->calcBound();
1901  liftLeftDoor->setTranslateX(liftLeftDoor->getTranslate().x + LIFT_SPEED);
1902  liftLeftDoor->calcBound();
1903  translateLiftX -= 0.1;
1904  }
1905  }
1906  // lift interaction - bring them to 2nd floor/ 1st floor
1907  static float doorTimer = 0;
1908  if(disableLiftDoor && translateLiftX <= 0) // Swap between floors after door closes
1909  {
1910  doorTimer += dt;
1911  if (doorTimer >= 1)
1912  {
1913  floorNum = newFloor;
1914  disableLiftDoor = false;
1915  doorTimer = 0;
1916  }
1917  }
1918  if(camera.position.x < supermarketLiftMaxBound.x && camera.position.x > supermarketLiftMinBound.x && camera.position.z < supermarketLiftMaxBound.z && camera.position.z > supermarketLiftMinBound.z)
1919  {
1920  if(keypressed[K_FIRST_FLOOR] && !disableLiftDoor)
1921  {
1922  if (floorNum != 1)
1923  {
1924  disableLiftDoor = true;
1925  newFloor = 1;
1926  }
1927  }
1928  if(keypressed[K_SECOND_FLOOR] && !disableLiftDoor)
1929  {
1930  if (floorNum != 2)
1931  {
1932  disableLiftDoor = true;
1933  newFloor = 2;
1934  }
1935  }
1936  }
1937  if(floorNum == 1) //1st floor
1938  {
1939  for(int a = 0;a<CharacterList.size();++a)
1940  {
1941 
1942  if (camera.position.x < supermarketDoorMaxBound.x && camera.position.x > supermarketDoorMinBound.x && camera.position.z < supermarketDoorMaxBound.z && camera.position.z > supermarketDoorMinBound.z||
1943  CharacterList[a]->getTranslate().x < supermarketDoorMaxBound.x && CharacterList[a]->getTranslate().x > supermarketDoorMinBound.x && CharacterList[a]->getTranslate().z < supermarketDoorMaxBound.z && CharacterList[a]->getTranslate().z > supermarketDoorMinBound.z)
1944  {
1945  if(translateX<2)
1946  {
1947  translateX+=0.1;
1948  --a;
1949  }
1950  }
1951 
1952  else
1953  {
1954  if(translateX>0)
1955  {
1956  translateX-=0.1;
1957 
1958  }
1959  }
1960  }
1961  }
1962  if(floorNum == 2)
1963  {
1964  if(camera.position.x < supermarketSecurityDoorMaxBound.x && camera.position.x > supermarketSecurityDoorMinBound.z && camera.position.z > supermarketSecurityDoorMinBound.z && camera.position.z < supermarketSecurityDoorMaxBound.z)
1965  {
1966  if(translateSecurityZ<2)
1967  {
1968  translateSecurityZ+=0.1;
1969  }
1970  }
1971  else
1972  {
1973  if(translateSecurityZ>0)
1974  {
1975  translateSecurityZ-=0.1;
1976  }
1977  }

3246 /******************************************************************************/
3255 /******************************************************************************/
3256 void SP2::RenderMesh(Mesh *mesh, bool enableLight)
3257 {
3258  Mtx44 MVP, modelView, modelView_inverse_transpose;
3259 
3260  MVP = projectionStack.Top() * viewStack.Top() * modelStack.Top();
3261  glUniformMatrix4fv(m_parameters[U_MVP], 1, GL_FALSE, &MVP.a[0]);
3262  if(enableLight)
3263  {
3264  glUniform1i(m_parameters[U_LIGHTENABLED], 1);
3265  modelView = viewStack.Top() * modelStack.Top();
3266  glUniformMatrix4fv(m_parameters[U_MODELVIEW], 1, GL_FALSE, &modelView.a[0]);
3267  modelView_inverse_transpose = modelView.GetInverse().GetTranspose();
3268  glUniformMatrix4fv(m_parameters[U_MODELVIEW_INVERSE_TRANSPOSE], 1, GL_FALSE, &modelView.a[0]);
3269 
3270  //load material
3271  glUniform3fv(m_parameters[U_MATERIAL_AMBIENT], 1, &mesh->material.kAmbient.r);
3272  glUniform3fv(m_parameters[U_MATERIAL_DIFFUSE], 1, &mesh->material.kDiffuse.r);
3273  glUniform3fv(m_parameters[U_MATERIAL_SPECULAR], 1, &mesh->material.kSpecular.r);
3274  glUniform1f(m_parameters[U_MATERIAL_SHININESS], mesh->material.kShininess);
3275  }
3276  else
3277  {
3278  glUniform1i(m_parameters[U_LIGHTENABLED], 0);
3279  }
3280  if(mesh->textureID > 0)
3281  {
3282  glUniform1i(m_parameters[U_COLOR_TEXTURE_ENABLED], 1);
3283  glActiveTexture(GL_TEXTURE0);
3284  glBindTexture(GL_TEXTURE_2D, mesh->textureID);
3285  glUniform1i(m_parameters[U_COLOR_TEXTURE], 0);
3286  }
3287  else
3288  {
3289  glUniform1i(m_parameters[U_COLOR_TEXTURE_ENABLED], 0);
3290  }
3291  mesh->Render();
3292  if(mesh->textureID > 0)
3293  {
3294  glBindTexture(GL_TEXTURE_2D, 0);
3295  }
3296 }

3298 /******************************************************************************/
3309 /******************************************************************************/
3310 void SP2::RenderText(Mesh* mesh, std::string text, Color color)
3311 {
3312  if(!mesh || mesh->textureID <= 0) //Proper error check
3313  return;
3314 
3315  //glDisable(GL_DEPTH_TEST);
3316  glUniform1i(m_parameters[U_TEXT_ENABLED], 1);
3317  glUniform3fv(m_parameters[U_TEXT_COLOR], 1, &color.r);
3318  glUniform1i(m_parameters[U_LIGHTENABLED], 0);
3319  glUniform1i(m_parameters[U_COLOR_TEXTURE_ENABLED], 1);
3320  glActiveTexture(GL_TEXTURE0);
3321  glBindTexture(GL_TEXTURE_2D, mesh->textureID);
3322  glUniform1i(m_parameters[U_COLOR_TEXTURE], 0);
3323  for(unsigned i = 0; i < text.length(); ++i)
3324  {
3325  Mtx44 characterSpacing;
3326  characterSpacing.SetToTranslation(i * 1.0f, 0, 0); //1.0f is the spacing of each character, you may change this value
3327  Mtx44 MVP = projectionStack.Top() * viewStack.Top() * modelStack.Top() * characterSpacing;
3328  glUniformMatrix4fv(m_parameters[U_MVP], 1, GL_FALSE, &MVP.a[0]);
3329 
3330  mesh->Render((unsigned)text[i] * 6, 6);
3331  }
3332  glBindTexture(GL_TEXTURE_2D, 0);
3333  glUniform1i(m_parameters[U_TEXT_ENABLED], 0);
3334  glEnable(GL_DEPTH_TEST);
3335 }
